'''JiaMo Fu''' (傅家谟, July, 1935 – June 11, 2015<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.sciencenet.cn/htmlnews/2015/6/320909.shtm |title=有机地球化学与沉积学家傅家谟院士逝世—新闻—科学网 |date=15 June 2015 |website=news.sciencenet.cn |access-date=2018-02-28}}</ref>) was an academician of the [[Chinese Academy of Sciences]] (CAS) and professor of environmental and architectural engineering in [[Shanghai University]]. He wrote about recycling electronic waste.<ref name="Simoneit">{{cite web|url=http://www.medicalnewstoday.com/articles/199230.php|title=Concern About Environmental Impact Of e-Waste Recycling|last=Simoneit|first=Bernd|date=30 August 2010|publisher=[[Medical News Today]]|accessdate=31 December 2010}}</ref>

